description:
This market will resolve to “Yes” if Valve launches Premier season 4 by January 31, 2026, 11:59 PM ET. Otherwise, this market will resolve to “No”.

Once launched, this market will remain open for 48 hours. Temporary launches (e.g., for testing) that are reversed within 48 hours will not count.

For the purpose of this market, “Valve” refers to Valve Corporation, the developer and publisher of the Counter-Strike series.

For the purpose of this market, “Premier season 4” refers to the fourth season of the Premier competitive matchmaking mode in Counter-Strike 2 (CS2), which consists of seasonal leaderboards, rank resets, and associated rewards eligible in Premier mode matchmaking.

The primary resolution source for this market will be official information from Valve; however, a consensus of credible reporting may also be used.
